## 8. Appendix

### Glossary

|  |  |
| --- | --- |
| Term | Definition |
| SBOM | Software Bill of Materials — inventory of all software components |
| CycloneDX | OWASP standard for SBOM format |
| SARIF | Static Analysis Results Interchange Format |
| OSV | Open Source Vulnerabilities database (Google) |
| Shannon Entropy | Measure of randomness/information density in a string |
| Misconfiguration | Insecure default or explicit setting that weakens security |

